node.text:
(Winner is: @vivika_19) 

Aurora resort / Norway GIVEAWAY!😍
We are giving you a chance to win a free stay at the magical resort @auroraborealisobservatory in Norway and a free entry to the brand new @romsdalsgondolen - a new way to experience the fantastic views of the mountains and fjords in Romsdalen, Norway🇳🇴

To enter: 
1. Follow @romsdalen.no & @romsdalsgondolen
2. Like this post
3. Tag a friend (1 tag = 1 entry, enter as many times as you wish).
4. (Bonus) Share this post on your IG Story for an additional entry!

The winner will be chosen randomly on 1 july 2021. Open internationally.
Good luck!! 💚
—
(This giveaway is not sponsored by Instagram)

node.text:
Norway GIVEAWAY! 🤩🇳🇴 We are giving you a chance to explore Lofoten Islands at @aarorbuer_lofoten and a free weekend stay at the magical resort @auroraborealisobservatory in Senja, Northern Norway. Breakfast included. 2 per. 
 To enter:
1. Sign up to the newsletter at www.arorbuer.no/newsletter
(link in bio)
2. Follow @aarorbuer_lofoten  3. Like this post 4. Tag a friend (1 tag = 1 entry, enter as many times as you wish).

(Bonus) Share this post on your IG Story for an additional entry!  The winner will be chosen randomly on 21. june 2021. Good luck!!💚🏔 -
(This giveaway is not sponsored by Instagram) - Any questions regarding this giveaway, contact @auroraborealisobservatory
-
Photo/video by:
@cathrinefagertun
@auroraborealisobservatory @aarorbuer_lofoten

node.text:
📍 La Jolla, San Diego, California 🇺🇸 
Pure wonder by @alec_basanec. When life throws you off tracks, hang on tight and keep in mind that there's a big, beautiful world out there for you to explore. 🌤

This awe-inspiring sight was shot in La Jolla, a charming seaside neighborhood in the city of San Diego known for its rugged coastline. Dubbed as "The Jewel of America’s Finest City", it offers sweeping panoramic ocean views, beautiful beaches, and sophisticated dining.

Have you ever heard of La Jolla and does this seem like your kind of place? 🌹

📽 @alec_basanec
🎶 God Complex (Instrumental) - Some Guy Ty

node.text:
📍Barcelona, Spain 🇪🇸
"This image was taken from Saragossa street in the Gràcia neighborhood of Barcelona. In the background, you can see the Tibidabo Mountain, the highest mountain in the city, standing at 512 meters high, and is home to the Church of the Sacred Heart of Jesus (Templo Expiatorio del Sagrado Corazón de Jesús) which was built in 1902-1961. Throughout the city, this is a benchmark skyline view as you stare at the mountain. From here, you can see some of the most beautiful views of Barcelona, from the sea to nearby attractions like an amusement park to enjoy a fun day with friends and family."

Have you experienced this view before while visiting Barcelona? Let us know about your experience in the comments below! 

📷@comomolabarcelona

node.text:
📍 Phi Phi Islands, Thailand 🇹🇭
Watch 'til the end to vicariously live through @sunny_rung's sunny vacation in the Phi Phi Islands. Offering vivid turquoise waters, beautiful beaches, and stunning rock formations, this small archipelago in Thailand is what tropical dreams are made of. 😍

Best of all, this paradise is accessible with just a 45-minute speedboat trip or a 90-minute ferryboat ride from either Phuket or Krabi! 🚤

Does this make you itch for a beach getaway? Tag who you want to take here! 🏝

📽 @sunny_rung
🎶 Ooh Ahh (My Life Be Like) - Grits Feat. Toby Mac
